[quote=“Tree, post:16, topic:210406”]Is this guy serious? Moronic individuals like you deserve to rot in the deep depths of Moparscape. It’s hilarious that you act in a condescending way towards us, when we are the heart and soul of this community. It’s because of us that you are still here.

It’s the internet children. It’s where people can be themselves with large amounts of anonymity and express any opinions that they have. It’s a world without laws, boundaries or limits. Such pornography is not restricted and therefore is different than what would usually be displayed in a world with boundaries/laws/limits. It’s odd because it is different. Grow up and learn to be more accepting or slightly more careless.

I have seen plenty of shock sites during my time on the internet. Nothing could possibly shock me anymore. Though i don’t agree or like some of the content of some sites, i don’t have a strong opposition to it. Done.[/quote]
Ok then
Well, we all agree that this thread was just a waste of time.
Time we could of spent doing other things.
Imagine…
